{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": {"link": "usage/", "title": "&lt;no title&gt;"}, "title": "Welcome to Llamda\u2019s Documentation", "meta": {"wordcount": {"words": 41, "minutes": 0}}, "body": "<section id=\"welcome-to-llamda-s-documentation\">\n<h1>Welcome to Llamda\u2019s Documentation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#welcome-to-llamda-s-documentation\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Llamda is a Python library that provides easy-to-use decorators for making your functions and Pydantic models compatible with Large Language Models (LLMs).</p>\n<section id=\"installation\">\n<h2>Installation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#installation\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>You can install Llamda using pip:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-bash notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>pip<span class=\"w\"> </span>install<span class=\"w\"> </span>llamda\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section id=\"quick-start\">\n<h2>Quick Start<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#quick-start\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Here\u2019s a simple example of how to use Llamda:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">llamda_fn</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Llamda</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">typing</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">llamda</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Llamda</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"nd\">@llamda</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">llamdafy</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">greet</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">times</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">int</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">&quot;&quot;&quot;Greet a person multiple times.&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"sa\">f</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Hello, </span><span class=\"si\">{</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"si\">}</span><span class=\"s2\">! &quot;</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">times</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Use the function</span>\n<span class=\"n\">result</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">greet</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Alice&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">result</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># Output: Hello, Alice! Hello, Alice! Hello, Alice!</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Get the JSON schema</span>\n<span class=\"n\">schema</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">llamda</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tools</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;greet&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">to_schema</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">schema</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"toctree-wrapper compound\">\n<p class=\"caption\" role=\"heading\"><span class=\"caption-text\">Contents:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"api_reference/\">API Reference</a><ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"api_reference/#llamda_fn.Llamda\"><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">Llamda</span></code></a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"api_reference/#llamda_fn.LlamdaFunctions\"><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">LlamdaFunctions</span></code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</section>\n", "metatags": "<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["py-modindex", "Python Module Index", "", "modules"], ["usage", "&lt;no title&gt;", "N", "next"]], "sourcename": "index.md.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Welcome to Llamda\u2019s Documentation</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#installation\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#quick-start\">Quick Start</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": true, "page_source_suffix": ".md", "current_page_name": "index", "sidebars": ["about.html", "navigation.html", "relations.html", "searchbox.html", "donate.html"], "alabaster_version": "0.7.16", "alabaster_version_info": [0, 7, 16]}